preview_comments.text: Kings. Will. Rise. 🤴🏿 Every man needs to practise improving the relationship that he has with himself first so that if and when a woman comes into his life it's a question of "it's either she improves the relationship that I already have with myself or I'm better off single!". Either she benefits your health and your values, Kings, or you live your life without her because, as men, we should be taking care of our health and upholding our values with or without a woman regardless!
That used to be me for many years! Fortunately I found terrific mentors that brought out my inner alpha and I am much better off!
